title: No longer stop the service.  Pretty sure that causes a race condition
message:
No longer stop the service.  Pretty sure that causes a race condition
where the service is fully killed before it has a chance to contact the backend.
Additionally the service can be restarted by the system, so we need to
check the intent to ensure it was requested in order to start the timer.
